  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Investigator investigated that regression of hamstring flexibility and performance in
      children with Duchenne Muscular Dystrophy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Flexibility of hamstrings was evaluated by Popliteal Angle test. Performance was evaluated 6
      Minute Walk Test (6 MWT). Regression of hamstring flexibility and performance was examined
      regression tests. Correlation was examined between popliteal angle test and parameter of
      North Star Ambulation Assessment.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
